PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1771894973
OL,3,C'We haven't forgotten you': Musicians
OL,4,Cmark fourth anniversary of war in
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FA police woman was killed, and dozens
OL,8,Fmore were injured. It was another
OL,9,Fexample of how every town and city in
OL,10,FUkraine is now, in reality, a civilian
OL,11,Ffrontline.
OL,13,FThat night, however, they were far
OL,14,Ffrom home, preparing to perform in a
OL,15,Fconcert in the tiny Cumbrian town of
OL,16,FKirkby Lonsdale, to mark the start of
OL,17,Fthe fifth year of this war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
