FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1771894973
OL,3,C'We haven't forgotten you': Musicians
OL,4,Cmark fourth anniversary of war in
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FBeneath the ancient beams of St Mary's
OL,8,FChurch, three members of the orchestra
OL,9,Fperformed with fellow musicians from
OL,10,Facross Lancashire and Cumbria.
OL,12,FTheir joint concert is designed to be
OL,13,Fa reminder of the deep affinity felt
OL,14,Ffor the Ukrainian people by those who
OL,15,Fhave the luxury of living in peace,
OL,16,Fnot war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
