PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1771894973
OL,3,C'We haven't forgotten you': Musicians
OL,4,Cmark fourth anniversary of war in
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FFor the orchestra, there is a huge
OL,8,Fsense of obligation to continue,
OL,9,Fhowever desperate the situation.
OL,10,FRussia's war effort has sought to
OL,11,Fdestroy much of Ukraine's distinct
OL,12,Fcultural heritage.
OL,14,FEvery member of the orchestra believes
OL,15,Fthey must continue to perform to
OL,16,Fsupport their countrymen and women and
OL,17,Fto ensure Ukraine's rich musical
OL,18,Fhistory continues into the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
