FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1771894973
OL,3,C'We haven't forgotten you': Musicians
OL,4,Cmark fourth anniversary of war in
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FHowever bad the overnight attacks,
OL,8,Fevery morning they are back to
OL,9,Frehearsals, believing in the
OL,10,Frestorative power of music for
OL,11,Fthemselves and others.
OL,13,FThey long for an end to the war and a
OL,14,Freturn to the lives they lived before.
OL,16,FIn Kirkby Lonsdale, they are fighting
OL,17,Fto keep their beautiful Norman church
OL,18,Fopen, knowing how crucial it is to
OL,19,Ftheir sense of community.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
