OL,3,C'We haven't forgotten you': Musicians
OL,4,Cmark fourth anniversary of war in
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FEach week, they pray for an end to
OL,8,FUkraine's war and now pray that when
OL,9,Fthat day comes, the Church will still
OL,10,Fbe open to welcome their Ukrainian
OL,11,Ffriends, to mark the end of this war,
OL,12,Fnot another dreadful milestone in it.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
